It works just fine!
there's only one thing: 
In the Signsis-GUI.exe application I used 
D:\route66\Route66 for Nokia N95\Route66 Software\Unsigned SIS\Route66.Mobile.v7.3.545.Multilanguage.S60v3.UnSigned.sis
as the input file. The application then fills in the output file:
D:\route66\Route66 for Nokia N95\Route66 Software\SIS\Route66.Mobile.v7.3.545.Multilanguage.S60v3.Unsigned_signed.sis
The path is slightly different (Unsigned SIS/ SIS folder) so it says there's an I/O problem. You can solve this by just manually altering the output path.

But thanks very much. Nice work!
